-- In Jersey there is not dispatcher servlet so we need to config the restService by extend ResourceConfig
   and register the resources class.
--
    @POST                          == request mapping
    @Path("/saveEmployee")         == request end point
    @Consumes("application/json")  == link : https://www.dineshonjava.com/using-consumes-and-produces-to/
    @Produces("application/json")  == link : https://www.dineshonjava.com/using-consumes-and-produces-to/